{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a2650485ba","title":"中央和中央文革首长接见西藏军区师以上干部代表时的指示","origin":"《中央文件汇编》，拉萨革命造反总部，1969年3月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4761f6fe6f","index":0,"year":1968,"month":8,"day":17,"articleId":"a2650485ba"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"40ffd466ef","name":"武斗","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"57eea82497","name":"康生","type":"人物"},{"id":"70a1e48626","name":"军队支左","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"82305e518c","name":"江青","type":"人物"},{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"cb4c84f4c0","name":"西藏文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"ef71f03227","name":"中央文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"185a577230","type":"title","text":"中央和中央文革首长接见西藏军区师以上干部代表时的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"266a361612","type":"subtitle","text":"（记录稿，未经首长审阅）","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"a32b73814a","type":"paragraph","text":"时间：1968年8月17日21时至18日1时05分。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"7765409c72","type":"paragraph","text":"地点：人民大会堂东大厅","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"3cae5d9835","type":"paragraph","text":"中央和中央文革首长：总理、伯达、康生、江青、春桥、富治、永胜、法宪、叶群、东兴、玉成。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"bace5bbd30","type":"paragraph","text":"当中央首长进入大厅时，同志们高呼口号：“敬祝毛主席万寿无疆！万寿无疆！万寿无疆！”“敬祝林副主席身体健康！永远健康！永远健康！”“我们要永远忠于毛主席！永远忠于毛泽东思想！永远忠于毛主席的革命路线！”“在以毛主席为首、林副主席为副的无产阶级司令部领导下，统一认识，统一步伐，统一行动！”“伟大领袖毛主席万岁！万岁！万万岁！”","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"e8f56240ad","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：同志们！今天开会，听听你们大家的意见，不同的意见，集中地说，说得短点。听了以后，我们再说点。以后见见你们的群众代表。5个省在8月份都要促上去，两个省已经批了，两个省的报告送来了，就剩你们西藏自治区了。（任荣：我们掉队了，掉的太远了。）不要紧，你们是最后解放的嘛！（笑）","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"b0b83f98a3","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：你们还可以往前赶嘛！（任荣同志开始汇报。）","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"0063448e3f","type":"paragraph","text":"当任荣同志谈到在重大的关键时刻都没处理好时。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"5a3829f9df","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你是什么时候来的？","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"e248685681","type":"paragraph","text":"（任荣：2月底来的，办训练班。）","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"4d0539a91d","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：6月6号不是讲的清清楚楚了吗？你传回去了吗？","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"5bd019e5a2","type":"paragraph","text":"（任荣：我们电报告诉，动用部队要经中央文革，电话不通了。）","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"1b9b97272c","type":"paragraph","text":"当任荣同志汇报到一五六团团长朱秀山问题时。","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"44047661e1","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：是团长？来了没有？","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"319a88d44f","type":"paragraph","text":"当任荣同志汇报到郭书科问题时。","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"3670c213d6","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：他不承认是支持“造总”的？","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"26491f6059","type":"paragraph","text":"（廖步云：“造总”观点。）","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"8acdcd0b5c","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：“造总”打“造总”观点的怎么解释？","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"5e196fa670","type":"paragraph","text":"（廖步云：生产部内部“大联指”观点打的。）","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"ffefde417c","type":"paragraph","text":"当汇报到对错误的认识，军区机关差些时。","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"5f7ef5c12a","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：常委内部怎么样？统一不统一？阴法唐来了没有？他还支持“大联指”观点，压“造总”吗？","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"bb0a4e79b7","type":"paragraph","text":"（任荣：廖副政委回去了，昨天才回来，他清楚。）","index":22,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"be7d357075","type":"paragraph","text":"当廖步云同志谈到对混进群众组织的坏人不很清楚时。","index":23,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"ed8a504756","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：石伴樵来了没有？","index":24,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"56837a93ad","type":"paragraph","text":"（石伴樵：来了。）（石站了起来。）","index":25,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"474d770f67","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：开始党委说徒手去，后来你改变了，带武器去，是怎么回事？","index":26,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"5c44db8855","type":"paragraph","text":"（石伴樵汇报带武器去的情况。）","index":27,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"41cb528371","type":"paragraph","text":"当张鹤田同志谈到带部队去财经大院这个行动本身就是错误的时。","index":28,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"7ef274325e","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你认为徒手去也是错误的？","index":29,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"e862a4281c","type":"paragraph","text":"（张鹤田：是的。）","index":30,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"399b0c6c87","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你是不是常委？","index":31,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"3680421418","type":"paragraph","text":"（任荣等：是党委委员。）","index":32,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"91f90975c2","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：当时在家主持工作的是那一位？","index":33,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"be8e30d9b6","type":"paragraph","text":"（赵文进：我。）","index":34,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"6445c9887d","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：当时你在？","index":35,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"9f3cd86b35","type":"paragraph","text":"（赵文进：我在。）","index":36,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"d6a454d0f5","type":"paragraph","text":"当赵文进同志谈到，当时规定是徒手，并交待千万不能开枪，不叫石伴樵去，因他同“造总”很对立时。","index":37,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"00eedefc86","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：西藏主要的矛盾是军队与群众组织的矛盾？还是群众组织之间的矛盾，军队在后面支持？","index":38,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"88c677224e","type":"paragraph","text":"（赵文进：我看主要是军队内部不统一。）","index":39,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"e74e8e78ac","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：常委一共几个人？都来了没有？你说的不统一，都以谁为代表？你能说出来吗？","index":40,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"b3c5e4008c","type":"paragraph","text":"（赵文进：来了6个。）","index":41,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"67e652f473","type":"paragraph","text":"当王亢同志谈到“6·7”事件，作为军区常委我有责任时。","index":42,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"13e0a57149","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：7号，中央军委转的毛主席关于加强军队组织纪律性的问题的指示，传回去了没有？","index":43,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"89e650fae4","type":"paragraph","text":"（王亢：当时还没有。）","index":44,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"c7a3b1bc4d","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：任荣继续说。","index":45,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"28b3d326c9","type":"paragraph","text":"当任荣同志谈到同“造总”关系紧张时。","index":46,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"2efd6d5f8f","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：支左第一线的是否同“造总”更对立些？","index":47,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"0031d8df45","type":"paragraph","text":"（任荣：石伴樵、丁永泰同志同“造总”比较对立，郑万兴、冯锦国同志同“造总”关系好些。）","index":48,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"1244de6810","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：住财经大院的是什么人，是商业部门的职员还是什么？","index":49,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"3596c82a71","type":"paragraph","text":"（廖步云：住的财粮厅、经计委……）","index":50,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"dcd9019d72","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：啊！经委、计委、财粮贸的机关干部。","index":51,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"76aa004f42","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：拉萨主要是机关干部。","index":52,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"0c4e6c850c","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：机关干部同部队连在一起，因为是一道进藏的嘛！北京学生还有没有？","index":53,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"9e323c3257","type":"paragraph","text":"（廖步云：没有。有各省的氓流。）","index":54,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"b5cbd17223","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：有多少？","index":55,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"c84130404f","type":"paragraph","text":"（王亢：原来200多，送回来一些，现在还有几十个。）","index":56,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"55b46d637f","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：那不算多了。","index":57,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"b05043ba98","type":"paragraph","text":"（任荣继续谈。）","index":58,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"0293b20290","type":"paragraph","text":"当任荣同志谈到支一派、压一派、亲一派、疏一派错误的关键在军区领导时。","index":59,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"3d9ca270cb","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：不限于“四大”单位吧！十一师是否倾向“造总”的多些？","index":60,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"46111bb3d7","type":"paragraph","text":"（任荣：关系好些。）","index":61,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"d64d194cf0","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：五十二师怎么样？是不是支持“大联指”的多些？","index":62,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"a4203532b8","type":"paragraph","text":"（任荣：对。下面的关系好些。）","index":63,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"ec44731c59","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：五十三师呢？","index":64,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"b3f8fe9039","type":"paragraph","text":"（任荣：是新组建的，有的干部有倾向，……）","index":65,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"64e52bb7f6","type":"paragraph","text":"伯达：国华同志同“造总”关系怎么样？","index":66,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"df785ec4c6","type":"paragraph","text":"（任荣：国华同志同“造总”关系好些。）","index":67,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"ec5d6c2861","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：去年1月他就支持“造总”。","index":68,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"85156412df","type":"paragraph","text":"（廖步云：他和两派都比较好，两派都对他有些意见，“大联指”意见多些。）","index":69,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"cbc5ca3486","type":"paragraph","text":"当任荣同志谈到同两派开了座谈会时。","index":70,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"e33141dab6","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：“造总”在北京有多少人？","index":71,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"c8f08004ec","type":"paragraph","text":"（任荣：100多人。）","index":72,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"d747eaf0f1","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：“大联指”呢？","index":73,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"cc4413810e","type":"paragraph","text":"（任荣：也有100多人。）","index":74,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"e7e5beb70a","type":"paragraph","text":"当任荣同志谈到拟对支左人员调整一下时。","index":75,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"a2994fb2e1","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：还没有轮换过吗？","index":76,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"4be065c6b1","type":"paragraph","text":"（任荣：准备调整一下，学习、提高。）","index":77,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"bf1b15c4cb","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：没有轮换，很大的数目没有参加支左。去年中央文革有个指示，你们大概没有执行这个。","index":78,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"e9e39e7a6c","type":"paragraph","text":"当曾雍雅同志谈到“造总”对周仁山问题已经统一了时。","index":79,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"17c0d4e291","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：这样好。“造总”有多少人？","index":80,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"af3a6d85ec","type":"paragraph","text":"（任荣等：自称20多万。“大联指”说他50万。）","index":81,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"b3bb1ab603","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：呀！把你们也包括进去了吧！（总理、康老笑）。“大联指”藏族多些吧？","index":82,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"22c103ceed","type":"paragraph","text":"（廖步云：专、县“大联指”占多数。）","index":83,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"7e21cd576e","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：各师的讲讲。十一师的讲讲，你们那位讲？","index":84,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"47926e0a1d","type":"paragraph","text":"（张瑞厚同志发言。）","index":85,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"33437321aa","type":"paragraph","text":"当张瑞厚同志谈到两派都是革命群众组织时。","index":86,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"21a6e38286","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：十一师几个团？","index":87,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"285ab0778a","type":"paragraph","text":"（张瑞厚：4个。）","index":88,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"9e3a59a36a","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：都住在拉萨吗？","index":89,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"043532711b","type":"paragraph","text":"（张瑞厚：在拉萨一个营。）","index":90,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"d0e008f2ff","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：那个团的？","index":91,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"c12aaf7c29","type":"paragraph","text":"（张瑞厚：三十二团的。）……当谈到去年7月份前，十一师基本倾向“大联指”时。","index":92,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"0458790ee4","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：“造总”去年搞了《专打土皇帝》。","index":93,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"102ceb414c","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：主要是打击了“造总”，抓了他们的人，关键在这个地方。当汇报到中央“9·18”指示两派都是革命群众组织时。","index":94,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"8ceb4d23f2","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：怎么？","index":95,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"b528cd58e9","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：去年9月18日在钓鱼台，有陈明义、任荣，张鹤田也来了吧！","index":96,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"80150f8470","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：周仁山也来了。","index":97,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"67f1fe64a1","type":"paragraph","text":"当谈到“6·7”事件部队开枪时。","index":98,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"707c9142d4","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：6月7日，7个连的建制，有没有你们师的？","index":99,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"1ebda65b90","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：6月7日，你们部队去了没有？","index":100,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"fff15651f7","type":"paragraph","text":"（张瑞厚：去了一个连，在围墙外面。）……当谈到部队同“造总”对立情绪很大时。","index":101,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"85d0246403","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：调你们支左的多少？","index":102,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"3c1c21f21a","type":"paragraph","text":"（张瑞厚：一个营，缺一个连。）……当谈到“6·7”采取了错误做法时。","index":103,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"847723f172","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：原财经大院有多少部队？","index":104,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"b9c8dc05f5","type":"paragraph","text":"（赵文进等：100多人。）","index":105,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"9b8af90e51","type":"paragraph","text":"当谈到大昭寺问题时。","index":106,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"6f768300e3","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：大昭寺是“造总”什么组织在？住的什么人？","index":107,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"edae46a4be","type":"paragraph","text":"（张瑞厚：“造总”四司和“红色广播站”。）","index":108,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"63657bd578","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：还有喇嘛没有？","index":109,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"171a9248d5","type":"paragraph","text":"（任荣：没有。）","index":110,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"2e7bd691c6","type":"paragraph","text":"当谈到大昭寺“造总”只61人时。","index":111,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"5d2f74d472","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：60多人，人很少嘛，“造总”总部在那里吗？","index":112,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"14d2e6b996","type":"paragraph","text":"（张瑞厚：是“造总”四司）。","index":113,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"24721234bb","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：大昭寺有没有别的部队？","index":114,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"1a135ddfbb","type":"paragraph","text":"（张瑞厚：在邮电局的一个班去了。……）","index":115,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"95bcbf055e","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你认为“6·7”事件是常委布署的，还是谁搞的？","index":116,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"7257a6c2ed","type":"paragraph","text":"（张瑞厚：军区有没有布置我不了解。）……当谈到拉萨长时间下午6、7点钟就戒严时。","index":117,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"1df6d872fc","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：尼泊尔领事馆的人受伤了吗？","index":118,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"eb7955c839","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：是部队打的，还是群众打的？","index":119,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"2ff42806aa","type":"paragraph","text":"（廖步云：那是7月份的事，是群众武斗打的。）","index":120,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"a91ebb02a8","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：呵！是7月份。田启元有什么意见？","index":121,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"d4c08d7496","type":"paragraph","text":"（田启元同志发言。）","index":122,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"81b85c5f23","type":"paragraph","text":"当郑万兴同志谈到被打时。","index":123,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"247375a781","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：6月3号你为什么被打？是“造总”打的，还是“大联指”打的？","index":124,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"4efc42f698","type":"paragraph","text":"（曾雍雅：不是，是军队内部打的。）","index":125,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"8bade7e7b5","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：那是“大联指”观点的！","index":126,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"1007920dec","type":"paragraph","text":"当郑万兴同志谈到送粮食为什么要带梯子时。","index":127,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"8d08364dcd","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：7月5号是怎么回事？还有“7·5”事件。“7·3”布告传去了没有？","index":128,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"37d23a6628","type":"paragraph","text":"（曾雍雅：当时没有。）","index":129,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"925b050819","type":"paragraph","text":"当廖步云同志汇报到“7·5”事件经过时。","index":130,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"ecd6ddb719","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：现在你们常委有两种意见。一种认为你们右了，对“造总”的坏人没按“7·3”布告执行，但敌情不清楚；一种是十一师政委的意见，是支一派、压一派的必然结果，是有计划的，怎么解释！张鹤田，你对十一师的意见，有什么看法，是不是有预谋的。","index":131,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"edc3047556","type":"paragraph","text":"（张鹤田：……）","index":132,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"33b580230c","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们内部在这个问题上还没谈一致。","index":133,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"33527c8ca2","type":"paragraph","text":"当任荣同志谈到下面的问题很难说时。","index":134,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"c8dad626d6","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：你好象一直在北京，让才来的同志讲讲，不好吗？","index":135,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"d78fde880d","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：五十二师的同志讲讲。","index":136,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"a8202cc7ea","type":"paragraph","text":"徐浩同志发言。当讲到军管会只能做一面工作时。","index":137,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"ca7893352f","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：在学习班两派情绪怎么样？可以谈到一块吗？有学习班的同志吗？谈一谈。当王德全同志谈到认识统一不起来时。","index":138,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"50b7b46bd1","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：是部队，还是群众？","index":139,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"11b699654e","type":"paragraph","text":"（王德全：部队事先解决的不好。）","index":140,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"4c9050cc0c","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你同两派能不能谈？","index":141,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"09b11c97e2","type":"paragraph","text":"（王德全：我还可以。）","index":142,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"9e5f0766fb","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你原先在那里，还超脱一点吧？","index":143,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"8217e64c81","type":"paragraph","text":"（王德全：……）","index":144,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"4b54efe5a2","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：今天是8月17号了，快8月18号了。在目前这个形势下，怎么推动革委会成立，推动一下怎么样？两派要求是否很急需？","index":145,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"bd80e60305","type":"paragraph","text":"当王德全同志谈到要求解决“6·7”问题时。","index":146,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"0e5523c487","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：正确解决“6·7”问题。拉萨群众有什么反映？","index":147,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"6e7348a593","type":"paragraph","text":"当王德全同志谈到“大联指”不参予这个问题时。","index":148,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"43d27087b9","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：也不表示意见吗？","index":149,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"9c35fdf1d7","type":"paragraph","text":"（王德全：……）","index":150,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"a26f6cdb17","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：在座的两派观点的同志，那派占多数。","index":151,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"0e1529d9d3","type":"paragraph","text":"（冯锦国同志要求发言……。）","index":152,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"159982dcc8","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：刚才他谈到5月份把他们调出来是事实吗？","index":153,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"a271f859bf","type":"paragraph","text":"当赵文进谈到打人止不住时。","index":154,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"2604801513","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：怎么部队打人就没办法了？","index":155,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"3838d27c7f","type":"paragraph","text":"（赵文进……）","index":156,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"33c7c4bfa7","type":"paragraph","text":"当冯锦国谈到家被抄时。","index":157,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"8b4ae7c7e1","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们是什么时候到北京的。","index":158,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"fa4793fd21","type":"paragraph","text":"（曾雍雅：我们是3月中旬来的。）","index":159,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"d67548b25f","type":"paragraph","text":"（任荣：我是2月底就来到学习班了。）","index":160,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"f515c27ab2","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：群众是不是抄了他的家？“6·6”接见时，我们发现阴法唐已经很偏了，为什么把他派回去，叫他回去，不是更偏向“大联指”了吗？为什么不叫他来？","index":161,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"39a177f49e","type":"paragraph","text":"康生、江青：是否抄了他的家？应当答复一下嘛！","index":162,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"31643eb18e","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：6月阴法唐是最偏的了，叫他回去，为什么不叫回来？他是支一派，压一派的代表嘛！张鹤田，你对阴法唐是什么看法？","index":163,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"10dd2b9c61","type":"paragraph","text":"（张鹤田：过去打仗、工作都很好，在文化大革命中是有错误的。）","index":164,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"5533fcf045","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：6月份我们发现他最偏。","index":165,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"7aac78ede1","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：他怎么回去哩！叫他在这里学习不更好吗？","index":166,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"14bf422180","type":"paragraph","text":"（任荣：当时考虑他对错误有认识，回去后可以做“大联指”的工作，在军管会说话也有人听……）","index":167,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"a76bc9c306","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：他对错误是不是有认识？大家说，他对错误认识怎么样？（常委有的同志回答：有进步。）常委以外的同志可以说话嘛！","index":168,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"228fbd01dd","type":"paragraph","text":"（宋开元发言，……）","index":169,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"634dfcd748","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：我问赵文进、王亢同志一个问题，4号要到财经大院去，接到北京常委电话，说调部队要经中央文革，是那天？","index":170,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"da88f63785","type":"paragraph","text":"（王亢：5号早晨。）","index":171,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"bc7372d4db","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：什么时候向中央发报请示的？拆墙有没有？","index":172,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"7c268c2074","type":"paragraph","text":"（王亢：我们请示了，拆墙有。）","index":173,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"eeff1d7c6c","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：你们接到北京电报犹豫了，既然请示了，为什么没按中央批准又行动？我不理解。你们不是不懂得，这里有个对待群众的问题，你们到底是听中央的，还是听谁的？","index":174,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"8694647c4c","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们的报告（拿起来，指“6·7”检查报告）就很难解释，既然知道要请示批准，没批准又行动。","index":175,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"941a6fa02c","type":"paragraph","text":"（张鹤田发言，……）","index":176,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"141d7b2c97","type":"paragraph","text":"（张桂森发言，……）","index":177,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"4d7347dd89","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：自己给自己脸上抹灰有什么好呢？如果打人打4次，在军队内部总不是光彩的事情，应当做自我批评，刚才我听的不是自我批评多了，而是自我批评太少了，几乎没有。还是按主席的教导多做自我批评，否则各靠各的，各说各的。“6·7”事件我不清楚，我正害感冒，你们在学习班自己去谈谈，出在部队内部不光彩，丢了人。","index":178,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"bbc297bc2f","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：吕义山同志，你没有表示态度，你也是2月份回来的？","index":179,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"475336ebca","type":"paragraph","text":"（吕义山……）","index":180,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"fad5b47cc0","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：“6·7”的检查报告，你们讨论没有？在军队内部能解决问题吗？","index":181,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"cd68ea9c04","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：听听不同意见，给大家商量一下。","index":182,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"bda2b818a4","type":"paragraph","text":"伯达：“大联指”观点的同志多听“造总”意见，“造总”观点的同志多听“大联指”意见，各自多作自我批评。","index":183,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"29405b6913","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：被打的应该这样想，这也是一种锻炼，说的过分一些，他们的心情可以理解，要作解释。","index":184,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"8e2f85812f","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：不能说不好说。各自多作自我批评，不然没办法。","index":185,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"706a40058d","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：现在不是国民党时代，我们是解放军嘛！","index":186,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"ef4474fed9","type":"paragraph","text":"伯达：你们要注意西藏敌情，有英国特务，印度特务，还有俄国的，国民党的。注意敌人是很重要的。","index":187,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"a7f5ce2cfc","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：俄国在那里搞的不久。","index":188,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"a6c71d2218","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：李毅是个什么人，他是参加黑会的，写过检讨。参加这个黑会的，有各式各样的情况，不要一律对待，他过去受了压迫，想找人支持。我不晓得他这个人有没有其他的想法，是否有意去搞反革命活动，还要区别对待。","index":189,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"7d49bad1aa","type":"paragraph","text":"（任荣：……）","index":190,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"137a797bfc","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：是不是一般干部？","index":191,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"5437e59f1c","type":"paragraph","text":"（曾雍雅：可能是22级。）","index":192,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"f329261553","type":"paragraph","text":"永胜：那是一般干部。","index":193,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"43f101d806","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：稿子（指“6·7”检查报告）要慎重，多征求大家意见，江青同志说，要多作自我批评，特别是常委要带头作自我批评，首先要解决军内问题。","index":194,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"a2862ef89f","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：拉萨情况不错嘛，形势很好，军内外都作了自我批评，陈明义做了，陶也做了，刘也做了。","index":195,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"4fad817c59","type":"paragraph","text":"永胜：军队要带头自我批评，什么这个观点，那个观点，必然要影响到社会两派。观点就是思想，就是毛泽东思想嘛！要统一起来，统一在以毛主席为首、林副主席为副的无产阶级司令部的周围，你们自己闹，就是给敌人送情报嘛！","index":196,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"3e85031a1e","type":"appellation","text":"伯达：军队要团结，各自多做自我批评。","index":197,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"856569083c","type":"paragraph","text":"法宪：你们是长期不团结，不解决，不揭发，不斗争，文化革命中带到社会，自己给自己脸上抹黑。","index":198,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"55d3abfc2e","type":"paragraph","text":"伯达：人民解放军应该成为藏族人民的榜样，团结的模范。","index":199,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"53801f85f0","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：电话还是不通，什么原因？","index":200,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"342848f3f5","type":"paragraph","text":"（任荣：……）","index":201,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"6e0a4477a3","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：要架临时线。","index":202,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"1ec377b7c3","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：是呵，可架临时线。","index":203,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"3db9d6fc3d","type":"paragraph","text":"伯达：藏族人民看到我们解放军内部不团结，他们是很奇怪。看到解放军支左工作中自己闹意见，很不理解。","index":204,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"837adb145e","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：是呵！解放军解放西藏，解放农奴，打叛匪，反击作战，很光荣嘛！在这场文化大革命中闹成这样，两个观点。当然，在“三支”“两军”中是有成绩的。","index":205,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"5bf30ebb41","type":"paragraph","text":"永胜：现在是时候了，该觉悟了，大敌当前，印度反动派在边界搞那样多部队，又有叛匪，你们不是不知道嘛！毛主席这么多最高最新指示，你们还不听，不好好学习，中央文革的指示不好好学习，搞这个观点，那个观点，怎么行。","index":206,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"87c71db610","type":"paragraph","text":"当有的同志谈到把群众组织的小报发到下边去时。","index":207,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"3f500708b3","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：把一派群众的报纸，都搞到连队去了。","index":208,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"5cc3e7525b","type":"paragraph","text":"永胜：不象话！是怎么搞的？","index":209,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"a29d98806f","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：《人民日报》、《解放军报》什么时候可以看到？","index":210,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"12d794e695","type":"paragraph","text":"（众答：10天到1月。）","index":211,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"3474cd9309","type":"paragraph","text":"永胜：他们主要靠半导体。","index":212,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"fed9e55d60","type":"paragraph","text":"伯达：今年生产还好吗？（任荣：农牧业生产还好！）西藏抓革命，促生产，促战备，有特殊意义。","index":213,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"a46f56ee2b","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：要认识文化大革命是一场政治大革命，这个问题要搞清楚。你们是打过很多仗的，是有功勋的。要统一于这个问题之下，这是两个阶级、两条道路、两条路线的斗争，要认识这个问题，抓好了两条路线的斗争，什么问题也好解决了。军队是无产阶级专政的柱石，但是不能对群众专政，不能镇压群众，只能保护群众。这是共产党同国民党根本区别的标志。公与私要搞清楚，公要放在上头。要好好总结经验，这样，西藏很有希望。坏人都弄掉了嘛！周仁山、王其梅这些。","index":214,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"376aed41b3","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：不要传，先在军队中讨论一下，不要贴大字报，传到200多人的两派去，不要闹笑话。最后解放的，不一定最后成立革委会嘛！可以提前嘛！","index":215,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"0a50cff697","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：你们争取早一点。","index":216,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"9b99c8bd42","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：今天是把其他事情向后推了，先解决你们的，你们要毛泽东思想挂帅，大道理管小道理，脑筋打开一点，问题就可以解决，大家说好不好？","index":217,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"df650ed5d9","type":"paragraph","text":"（众答：好！）","index":218,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"},{"id":"856a9cc05b","type":"paragraph","text":"最后，同志们高呼口号：“感谢中央和中央文革首长对我们的亲切关怀！”“对中央和中央文革首长的指示，要认真学习，坚决贯彻！坚决照办！”“誓死保卫毛主席！”“誓死保卫林副主席！”“誓死保卫党中央！”“誓死保卫中央文革！”“誓死保卫江青同志！”“认真开展自我批评！”“团结起来，共同对敌！”“无产阶级文化大革命全面胜利万岁！”“毛主席的革命路线胜利万岁！”“战无不胜的毛泽东思想万岁！”“伟大领袖毛主席万岁！万岁！万万岁！”到会同志热烈鼓掌欢送，中央首长向同志们频频招手致意。","index":219,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba"}],"page":{"id":"c61c2a3851","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a2650485ba","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}